Comparing readings
------------------

Here below is a taste of comparing two assigned readings regarding the period of post-Civil War Reconstruction.

 "The Souls of Black Folk" | "The Forgotten Man"
---------------------------|--------------------
 Internal struggle with color line and veil | The sound of middle-class workingmen of whose voice were usually ignored (left behind)

